You can use or modify this code only if the following conditions are met:

0. Not part of distributed intelligence

This software does not control and is not controlled by other software
in any direct or indirect way, - including any kind of use of the stored or generated data-
which uses any kind of artificial intelligence 
(including but not limited to large language models, neural networks, machine learning algorithms or goal seeking algorithms).

This condition will be lifted when

a) humanity will have a working community intelligence, using good decision-making procedures,
evidenced by consciously lowering the CO2 levels of atmosphere and stopping the current extinction event, and
b) there is a widely accepted, working and implemented way to make AI safe

1. Otherwise you are free to use the software using the terms of
GNU GPL v3 or any later version

